Te llegué a entender, nena,
pero te perdí al final.

974
00:48:17,640 --> 00:48:18,800
Oye, oye.

975
00:48:18,840 --> 00:48:20,360
Hola, tío Phil.

976
00:48:20,400 --> 00:48:21,920
Aquí tienes.

977
00:48:21,960 --> 00:48:23,040
Ponme una.

978
00:48:23,080 --> 00:48:24,000
Para ti.

979
00:48:24,040 --> 00:48:25,920
Toma, para ti.

980
00:48:25,960 --> 00:48:27,280
Toma, para ti.

