00:49:54,640 --> 00:49:56,520
SI LA DEJARON MARCHAR...

1013
00:49:56,520 --> 00:49:58,680
...CREO QUE NOSOTROS
TAMBIEN DEBERIAMOS.

1014
00:49:58,720 --> 00:50:00,200
VAMOS

